<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If a publicly traded company owns a television=
 network and uses it to make false claims=C2=A0about rigged US elections, i=
s that securities fraud? Uh, I mean, technically <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31193834.260451/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
LmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDQtMTEvZm94LWNvbnNwaXJhY3ktdGhlb3JpZXMtc3B=
