or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">  this is a shareholder derivative lawsuit</a>, but I=E2=80=99m going=
 to count it:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A Fox Corp. investor sued Rupert M=
urdoch and his son Lachlan on Tuesday, blaming them for allowing Fox News t=
o spread lies about the election and prompting the [Dominion] defamation ca=
se. Delaware=E2=80=99s Chancery Court suit accuses the Murdochs and three o=
ther Fox directors of =E2=80=9Cknowingly=E2=80=9D hosts and guests to sprea=
d Trump=E2=80=99s false stolen-election claims.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/31193834.260451/aHR0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb2N1bWVu=
